  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We knew that he has broken his ribs in an accident.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We knew his size of the-- of the head.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We knew the way how-- how the teeth, the number of his shoes, and all these kind of-- there was about 12 question that it has to be the same.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And we knew the number of his SS number, not only here, but [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "It was here also.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "So-- and then, after following him, a few weeks before, and then I came there, and I saw him how he walked and what car he goes.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I knew his children.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I knew the small boy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I knew the place.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "It was raining.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "It was winter at the time, very-- very cold.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And it could be very cold days in the-- in Buenos Aires.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I was laying there in the water, not once, with my binoculars and looking into there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I saw him, how he lives, how the woman, and how he likes the small boy.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I said, maybe we are mistaken.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "How could it be that Eichmann loves so the small child and loves his family is the man who killed so many people?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You never know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I said, maybe we're mistaken.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The name is Ricardo Klement.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Everybody knows him as Ricardo Klement.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Well, the question-- the question mark.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we didn't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But then, it came to all the-- if we are going after him, if we're following him anymore, it will be a catastrophe, because something will happen, that he will feel.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because it was a place that you don't have a reason to stay there in San Fernando in the Garibaldi Street, and a place that every-- everybody knows everybody.",
      "word_count": 29
    }
